<p><p>&ldquo;It was a hard thing to hear as a 16-year old,&rdquo; Price said. Those who struggle with the disorder, or want to learn about it, can join the Newport News Democrat Tuesday at 7 p.m. for&nbsp;<a href="https://us06web.zoom.us/meeting/register/tZIvdOipqjsvGdGbUFWStgqav06k-KfbhWkh" target="_blank">a virtual discussion</a>. Price and three other speakers will be talking about their experiences and sharing ways to advocate for those with PCOS.</p>
