<h3 id="prices-statement-on-the-heritage-high-school-shooting">Price's statement on the Heritage High School Shooting</h3>
<p><p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="/images/30630/custom_logo_2552cead094d4c65843d497ba7c071b0.png" style="top: 229px; width: 291.4px; height: 51.2px;" class="image-align-center" />Del. Price's statement on today's events:</p>
